{{monster info|Vampire}}
==Useful Info==
'''Vampires''' are [[undead]] opponents who focus on nefarious, backhanded attacks to defeat their enemies. They are occasionally found in the middle floors of [[the Dungeon]].

{{monster spells|Vampire}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*An invisible vampire can be difficult to fight. They are hard to hit, constantly steal health, and deal moderately high damage. Being [[confuse]]d only makes it harder for you to hit one. High [[willpower]] and [[see invisible]] are both helpful when vampires are around.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.12]], vampires had the [[Vampire Summon]] spell, a monster-only version of [[Summon Small Mammals]] that could potentially produce [[orange rat]]s.
